IC by providing support, creating opportunities, measuring success, and building community.  Core functions:   Career development  Community building  Measuring success  Administrative support   If you are a new postdoc at UIC, check out our ‘ For New Postdocs ’ page where you can find information on how to settle in at UIC.  Make sure to stay tuned with our activities by joining the listserv and other social media platforms.      Resources        OPA Newsletters          Travel Awards           Open Postdoc Positions       Cancer Biology Postdoc Position    Posted on April 07, 2020          T32 Call for Postdoctoral Applications: Lung Biology and Pathobiology Training Program    Posted on April 07, 2020             Announcements and Events       Information for Campus Research Restart    Posted on April 28, 2020        CCTS Pilot Funding for COVID-19    Posted on April 14, 2020        Office of the Vice Chancellor for Research UPDATE – Friday, March 20, 2020 - 5:25pm    Posted on March 20, 2020        Office of the Vice Chancellor for Research UPDATE – March 19, 2020, 4:25pm    Posted on March 19, 2020        COVID-19 Office of the Vice Chancellor for Research Update - March 17, 2020    Posted on March 17, 2020           Jul  31  2020      UIC Postdoctoral Fellow Travel Award (Travel Period 9/1 to 11/30)     Friday, 5:00 pm–5:00 pm                Postdoctoral Scholars    Back to main content           About Us     Postdoctoral Association    Office of Postdoctoral Affairs     OPA Newsletters      Contact Us      For New Postdocs     Postdoc Orientation      Career Development     Career development Symposium    Postdoc Workshop Series    Career Development Resources      Events    Funding Opportunities     UIC Postdoctoral Fellow Travel Award Policy & Guidelines    External Opportunities      Administrative Support    Community     Annual Survey    Newsletter                     UIC Logo         Office Of  The Vice  Chancellor  For  Research                   Conta